{"tid":2116084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咩都明白，但真係好撚心碎","createTime":"2020-07-20T02:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T06:29:03.000Z","uid":105350,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"439a4851e7dedf2f3aaff43b875c74e1afa46866","tid":2116084,"uid":105350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:51:06.000Z","msg":"冇咗你，我好似冇咗全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日起身都好空虛好不安！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日只係想喊，喊完又再喊！<br />\n你話我唔明，我其實所有野都明白<br />\n只係我做唔到！你可以覺得我好矛盾，但我唔想嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住，我都好心碎。<br />\n呼吸都覺得好痛，你話你之前都係咁，但我宜家真係唔一樣，唔係正常嘅狀況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n初步有焦慮症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52683fecc6dc26945cf828c2189a6e1277551470","tid":2116084,"uid":124277,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a7c17d313e7c0934eda6fd115ce10f33eb8d72b","tid":2116084,"uid":23087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"輸了你 贏了世界又如何"},{"pid":"581bd6743f7056708feafcfd1191a1161974a415","tid":2116084,"uid":105350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52683fecc6dc26945cf828c2189a6e1277551470","tid":2116084,"uid":124277,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇試過不安到抽筋，手腳啲肌肉都控制唔到自己抽筋？"},{"pid":"d7c60a141a5eb7ef3fe3cf3c36e90de7db1c95ea","tid":2116084,"uid":105067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e